A unique armor designed by the [[Baragwin/Legends|Baragwin]], '''Baragwin Shadow Armor''' was a modifiable suit of [[Armor/Legends|armor]] that enhanced the capabilities of most [[Stealth field generator/Legends|stealth fields]], allowing the wearer to almost seamlessly blend in with their surroundings. Though generally sold only to respected governmental agencies, during the [[Jedi Civil War]] a few units popped up in the black market.

